<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - No Encontrado | Prestoflux</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" />
</head>

<body class="bg-[#f3f4f9] min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center font-sans">

    <div class="w-full max-w-lg p-6 text-center">
        <div class="mb-10 animate__animated animate__pulse animate__infinite">
            <div class="relative inline-block">
                <span class="text-[150px] font-black text-slate-200 tracking-tighter leading-none">404</span>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-search text-indigo-600 text-6xl drop-shadow-xl"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">¡Ups! Página no encontrada</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            Parece que la ruta <code
                class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 px-2 py-1 rounded font-mono text-sm"><%= typeof url !== 'undefined' ? url : 'solicitada' %></code>
            no existe o ha sido movida temporalmente.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/dashboard"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200 transition-all transform active:scale-95">
                <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i> Ir al Dashboard
            </a>

            <button onclick="history.back()"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 text-slate-600 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all shadow-sm">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i> Volver atrás
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
                SISTEMA DE CONTROL INTERNO PRESTOFLUX
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>